0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得經agent比佢地食人工<br />\n點解唔自己親力親為搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你做邊行 有啲行業係好多<br />\n例如it 連政府都帶頭經agent請人"},{"pid":"01e55ca5c003da8516effd5875afb9815841267b","tid":494043,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得經agent比佢地食人工<br />\n點解唔自己親力親為搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜agent唔係收番請你間公司既錢咋咩 你冇蝕架喎搵佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b949be35d45eeac8707ded2e8ea6cffdda98c90","tid":494043,"uid":13809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"Perm = 收公司錢，約你年薪既20%<br />\nContract = 食公司budget同你人工既差價"},{"pid":"eb523c54fbb90b5f560a4ffbbf068e66b37b142e","tid":494043,"uid":17667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打可唔可以介紹係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前搵左一個完全唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你搵邊行啊？佢地係根據行業分team</blockquote><br />\n我搵financial services <br />\n你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429ac318ae147eb4c9ef762b453ed6f477f75202","tid":494043,"uid":86442,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"叫呢間野食屎啦<br />\n打電話話我上去interview,問極係咩position 唔肯答<br />\n上到去講唔夠5分鐘，英文講左5句就話我英文唔得<br />\n冇可能做到我想做既「高級公司」既工<br />\n跟手塞我去做Asia Miles 既hotline <br />\n我reject就黑面<br />\n<br />\n去到最後我宜家就係做緊佢口中「高級公司」既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：在台北同美國都做過野"},{"pid":"fba05e57c53d252d53e617638971b67abf5f42f1","tid":494043,"uid":71679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫呢間野食屎啦<br />\n打電話話我上去interview,問極係咩position 唔肯答<br />\n上到去講唔夠5分鐘，英文講左5句就話我英文唔得<br />\n冇可能做到我想做既「高級公司」既工<br />\n跟手塞我去做Asia Miles 既hotline <br />\n我reject就黑面<br />\n<br />\n去到最後我宜家就係做緊佢口中「高級公司」既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：在台北同美國都做過野</blockquote><br />\n我年幾前上過去interview   佢話我expected salary太高   咁樣好難搵工   壓到我得返current salary 再高1.5k左右    我轉過頭自己上jb 搵唔經agent   搵左一陣已經有expected salary果個數  title仲要唔差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa94c0d265679cad746d8c29b7bfe87fdf1aa0a2","tid":494043,"uid":103514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"試過一次，上去佢地金鐘office見負責個agent<br />\n傾完計，第二個星期已經幫手約到請人間公司 interview，算係咁<br />\n不過最後自己衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 通常如果請正式長工，佢地啲commission係取決於間公司最後幾錢請你，所以幫你嗌高對佢地都有好處的"},{"pid":"5e97bc62c6a74fbc8058ba5d215aed370f649f2a","tid":494043,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0e3be40f0807bd39ea78febe273b118a69b187","tid":494043,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人食撚左你佣都唔知啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你以為你劉華個仔定城城個親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdbb6e0b1ed929020b904eaf5e542a6fe59ff94","tid":494043,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/asset